reviewText: Very informative, A nice addition to my cooking collection dvd's.
Owned this before a good all around sampling of fresh water fish that I catch on inland lakes here and are sold in my market place. The chef was first class a mans man with his presentations.
If you like wild game for table fare then you need to get this video.  Chef Milos covers the material well and shows you how to make a safe and tasty transition from field to table.  Bon Appetite!
